            "indent": 0,
            "type": "link",
            "rel": null,
            "target": null,
            "title": null,
            "url": "__GHOST_URL__/articles/news/classic-restored-after-fire/",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". Also claimed by the fire was a 1959 Morris Minor and a 1967 MGB. All three are historically important cars. Each is a collectible and while they can be replaced, they had tremendous sentimental value.",
