            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " in fires, both in California and elsewhere. And while it’s great to hear nobody was hurt, including the couple’s four cats and dog, it’s still sad to see such beautiful cars unnecessarily ruined. We’ll be fair and say it’s also tragic that their home burned down, but we’re a collector car site first ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
